WEBVTT

00:01.068 --> 00:02.636
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:02.669 --> 00:05.706
Celia: MY DAUGHTER
IS NOT MODELING FAT CLOTHES.

00:05.739 --> 00:07.174
Man:
SHE'S FANTASTIC.

00:07.207 --> 00:08.475
I HAVE A JOB INTERVIEW.

00:08.509 --> 00:09.610
WHO'S REJECTING YOU TODAY?

00:09.643 --> 00:13.313
AFTER MY UNCLE PAID HER,
JADE TOOK ME INTO A ROOM...

00:13.347 --> 00:14.348
Shh!

00:15.916 --> 00:17.851
YOU'RE ADORABLE,
BUT I'M NOT ATTRACTED TO YOU.

00:17.885 --> 00:19.286
HEYLIA?
JOSEPH.

00:19.319 --> 00:20.587
I'D VERY MUCH
LIKE TO SEE YOU.

00:20.621 --> 00:23.056
Conrad: THESE ARE OUR
POT‐GROWIN' ARMENIAN NEIGHBORS.

00:23.090 --> 00:24.191
I HAVE THIS PROBLEM.

00:24.224 --> 00:25.559
I'VE GOT TO
GET BACK TO WORK.

00:25.592 --> 00:26.593
IT'S A RAID.

00:26.627 --> 00:27.728
WE GOT TO HIDE IT ALL!

00:27.761 --> 00:29.863
Woman: THE DARING RAID
TOOK PLACE LATE LAST NIGHT...

00:29.897 --> 00:32.466
YOU GOT ME A NEIGHBORHOOD.
I DID.

00:32.499 --> 00:34.301
Man: KEEP HIM AWAY
FROM MY DAUGHTER.

00:34.334 --> 00:35.936
SHE MEETS YOUR SON,
SHE STARTS SMOKING POT,

00:35.969 --> 00:37.437
AND SHE'S HAVING ABORTIONS.

00:37.471 --> 00:38.539
JUST DRIVE.

00:39.940 --> 00:43.143
