01:03.630 --> 01:06.934
♪♪ AND THEY ALL LOOK
JUST THE SAME ♪♪

01:06.967 --> 01:08.969
♪♪ AND THE PEOPLE IN THE HOUSES ♪♪

01:09.002 --> 01:11.905
♪♪ ALL WENT TO UNIVERSITIES ♪♪

01:11.939 --> 01:14.074
♪♪ WHERE THEY WERE PUT
IN BOXES ♪♪

01:14.107 --> 01:16.944
♪♪ AND THEY CAME OUT
ALL THE SAME ♪♪

01:16.977 --> 01:19.746
♪♪ AND THERE'S DOCTORS
AND LAWYERS ♪♪

01:19.780 --> 01:21.448
♪♪ AND BUSINESS EXECUTIVES ♪♪

01:21.481 --> 01:24.818
♪♪ AND THEY'RE ALL MADE OUT
OF TICKY‐TACKY ♪♪

01:24.852 --> 01:31.124
♪♪ AND THEY'RE ALL
JUST THE SAME ♪♪

01:36.330 --> 01:39.132
[ KICKS DOOR ]
SILAS. COME ON.

01:39.166 --> 01:42.736
YOU CAN'T STAY
LOCKED IN THERE FOREVER.

01:42.769 --> 01:45.172
AT LEAST COME OUT AND IGNORE ME.

01:45.205 --> 01:48.842
OR LET LUPITA
REFUSE TO CHANGE YOUR SHEETS.

01:48.876 --> 01:50.611
Silas: GO AWAY.

01:50.644 --> 01:53.714
I WANT TO TALK.

01:53.747 --> 01:57.150
[ SIGHS ]
COME OUT AND TALK TO ME.

01:57.184 --> 01:59.386
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

02:02.689 --> 02:03.724
HELLO?

02:03.757 --> 02:05.259
WE GOT TROUBLE
IN LITTLE ARMENIA.

02:05.292 --> 02:07.528
WOULD IT KILL YOU TO SAY
GOOD MORNING WHEN YOU CALL?

02:07.561 --> 02:09.363
I AIN'T SO SURE
IT'S A GOOD MORNING.

02:09.396 --> 02:11.031
THE DEA...

02:13.767 --> 02:16.436
THE DEA KNOCKED OVER
SOME GROW HOUSES NEAR OUR SPOT.

02:16.470 --> 02:17.571
WHO WAS ON SHIFT?

02:17.604 --> 02:18.672
SANJAY.

02:18.705 --> 02:19.907
YOU HEAR FROM HIM?

02:19.940 --> 02:21.308
NO, BUT ‐‐

02:21.341 --> 02:23.243
JUST MEET ME OVER HERE.
WE GONNA GO IN TOGETHER.

02:23.277 --> 02:25.312
OKAY.
I'LL BE THERE SOON.

02:41.862 --> 02:44.498
SOMETHIN' AIN'T RIGHT.

02:44.531 --> 02:47.167
WHAT HAPPENED?

02:49.837 --> 02:51.405
THEY MUST'VE BUSTED SANJAY.

02:51.438 --> 02:54.074
OH, NO. NO. NO.

02:56.343 --> 02:59.146
[ DIALING ]

02:59.179 --> 03:02.583
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

03:10.123 --> 03:11.892
[ CELLPHONE RING INTENSIFIES ]

03:11.925 --> 03:13.393
AHHH! DON'T SHOOT!

03:15.562 --> 03:17.397
OH. HI.

03:18.799 --> 03:19.867
HANG ON, OKAY?

03:19.900 --> 03:21.034
I'VE GOT A CALL.

03:23.704 --> 03:24.838
HELLO?

03:24.872 --> 03:27.741
WHAT THE FUCK HAPPENED?!

03:27.774 --> 03:30.544
WE THOUGHT WE WERE BEING BUSTED.
WE TRIED TO FLUSH THE WEED.

03:30.577 --> 03:32.346
YOU THINK A HOUSEFUL OF WEED
IS LIKE A DIME BAG

03:32.379 --> 03:33.747
IN THE BOYS' ROOM
AT CHURCH CAMP?

03:33.780 --> 03:35.115
I'M HINDU.

03:35.148 --> 03:36.850
WE? WHO'S WE?
ANDY.

03:36.884 --> 03:37.885
WHERE IS HE?

03:37.918 --> 03:39.253
I DON'T KNOW.

03:39.286 --> 03:41.822
HE JUST YELLED, "OUT OF MY WAY,
BROWNIE," AND RAN OFF.

03:41.855 --> 03:43.257
WHERE THE FUCK
IS MY MOTHER?

03:43.290 --> 03:44.057
ANDY HAD IT.

03:44.091 --> 03:45.359
LISTEN, I HAVE TO GO.

03:45.392 --> 03:46.960
MY MOM
IS PROBABLY FLIPPING OUT.

03:46.994 --> 03:49.062
GO. GO. GO. GO.

03:53.667 --> 03:54.835
WHAT, NO RAID?

03:54.868 --> 03:56.303
MOTHERFUCKER.

03:57.104 --> 03:58.972
I THINK
WE NEED A PANIC ROOM.

03:59.006 --> 04:00.841
WHAT'D YOU DO?

04:00.874 --> 04:02.276
WE CAN'T SEE OUT, OKAY?

04:02.309 --> 04:05.479
AND THERE WERE SIRENS
AND HELICOPTERS, SO I PANICKED.

04:05.512 --> 04:08.315
IF WE HAD A PANIC ROOM,
I WOULDN'T HAVE PANICKED.

04:08.348 --> 04:10.184
WHY DOES MY PLANT
SMELL FUNNY?

04:10.217 --> 04:11.385
BECAUSE I SAVED IT.

04:11.418 --> 04:15.222
BY THE WAY, I'M A LITTLE
FREAKED OUT OVER HERE.

04:15.255 --> 04:17.824
THOUGHT I WAS GOING TO JAIL.

04:17.858 --> 04:19.092
LOOK AT THIS FACE.

04:19.126 --> 04:20.460
I'D GET PASSED AROUND PRISON
LIKE A LOOSE JOINT.

04:20.494 --> 04:22.829
SMELLS LIKE PISS.
DID YOU PISS ON MY PLANT?

04:22.863 --> 04:24.865
NO, I DID NOT PISS
ON YOUR PLANT.

04:24.898 --> 04:26.066
I WATERED IT WITH MY URINE.

04:26.099 --> 04:28.669
YOU WHAT?
I WAS SAVING HER LIFE.

04:28.702 --> 04:31.605
NOT ONLY DID I PROVIDE MOISTURE
WHEN SHE WAS DRY,

04:31.638 --> 04:33.841
BUT I WRAPPED HER PRECIOUS ROOTS
IN MY GOOD HOODIE, SO...

04:33.874 --> 04:35.809
YOU'RE WELCOME.

04:35.843 --> 04:36.844
YOU PISSED IN MY PLANT.

04:36.877 --> 04:38.679
PEE HAS NITROGEN IN IT.

04:38.712 --> 04:40.147
MAN, THAT'S GOOD FOR PLANTS.

04:40.180 --> 04:42.349
NOT WHEN IT'S CONCENTRATED,
LIKE IN PEE.

04:42.382 --> 04:44.618
IT WASN'T CONCENTRATED.
I DRANK SEVEN BOTTLES OF WATER.

04:44.651 --> 04:47.387
I KNOW THE IMPORTANCE
OF STAYING HYDRATED, MAN.

04:47.421 --> 04:49.056
IS THIS BAD FOR US?

04:49.089 --> 04:52.459
DID HE HURT OUR PLANT
WITH HIS PEE?

04:52.492 --> 04:55.896
SEE? SHE'S LOOKING PRETTY GOOD,
ISN'T SHE?

04:55.929 --> 04:57.898
THAT IS A LITTLE BIT OF ME
IN HER.

04:57.931 --> 04:59.733
WHY DO YOU NEVER KNOW
WHEN TO SHUT UP?

04:59.766 --> 05:02.703
GET HER BACK IN SOME SOIL AND
SEE IF SHE'LL TAKE ROOT AGAIN.

05:02.736 --> 05:05.105
IF SHE DOES,
WE'RE OKAY, RIGHT?
HE FUCKED UP OUR LIGHTS.

05:05.138 --> 05:07.641
YOU BETTER HOPE THAT THE REST
OF THEM PLANTS ARE OKAY.

05:07.674 --> 05:10.811
I'M GONNA GO CLIP SOME CLONES
AND GET US BACK ON TRACK.

05:10.844 --> 05:11.945
[ SIGHS ]

05:11.979 --> 05:13.380
AT LEAST WE'RE STILL
IN BUSINESS, RIGHT?

05:13.413 --> 05:14.748
WE COULD ALL BE
IN THE HOOSEGOW RIGHT NOW.

05:14.781 --> 05:18.218
NO, WE COULDN'T. WE WERE FINE
TILL YOU TRASHED THE PLACE.

05:22.723 --> 05:24.024
I'M GONNA GO CHECK THE POTTY,

05:24.057 --> 05:26.727
SEE IF ANY OF THE OTHER CLONES
ARE SALVAGEABLE.

05:29.062 --> 05:32.132
YEAH, YOU DO THAT.

05:34.868 --> 05:36.036
NICE. HMM?

05:36.069 --> 05:38.405
YOU LOOK ADORABLE, HONEY.

05:38.438 --> 05:40.507
ISN'T THIS EXCITING?
IT'S EXCITING.

05:40.541 --> 05:41.742
YEAH, IT IS.

05:41.775 --> 05:43.076
[ DRILL WHIRRS ]

05:44.044 --> 05:45.412
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

05:45.445 --> 05:48.081
WELL, THIS IS NOW
OUR ONLY SOURCE OF INCOME,

05:48.115 --> 05:50.250
SO I'M PROTECTING OUR ASSETS.

05:50.284 --> 05:51.084
EXCUSE ME.

05:51.118 --> 05:53.220
THE HAIR IS ALL WRONG.

05:53.253 --> 05:56.757
SHE HAS A SMALL HEAD
ON A LARGE BODY.

05:56.790 --> 05:58.125
DON'T LET THE MOON FACE
FOOL YOU.

05:58.158 --> 06:01.795
SHE NEEDS HER BIG HAIR
TO BALANCE THINGS OUT.

06:01.828 --> 06:03.163
THIS IS
WHAT THE DIRECTOR WANTS.

06:03.197 --> 06:05.566
WELL, THE DIRECTOR
DOESN'T REALIZE

06:05.599 --> 06:08.435
THAT ISABEL
HAS A FREAKISHLY SMALL HEAD.

06:08.468 --> 06:09.369
MOM.

06:09.403 --> 06:11.638
I AM LOOKING OUT
FOR YOUR BEST INTEREST.

06:11.672 --> 06:12.539
EXCUSE ME.

06:12.573 --> 06:17.845
IF YOU ADD A LITTLE VOLUME
TO THE HAIR...

06:17.878 --> 06:20.113
SHE WON'T LOOK LIKE A PINHEAD.

06:20.147 --> 06:22.316
I DON'T NEED
THESE NEGATIVE VIBES.

06:22.349 --> 06:25.085
WELL, THAT HAIRDRESSER SHOULD BE
STYLING HAIR AT THE CIRCUS.

06:25.118 --> 06:26.453
YOU WANT TO HAVE A GO
WITH MAKEUP NEXT

06:26.486 --> 06:27.754
JUST TO GUARANTEE
THAT SHE'S FIRED?

06:27.788 --> 06:29.923
WELL, THE MAKEUP IS TERRIBLE,
TOO.

06:29.957 --> 06:32.259
I MEAN, WHO GIVES
AN 11‐YEAR‐OLD BLOW‐JOB LIPS?

06:32.292 --> 06:33.694
WHAT SEEMS
TO BE THE PROBLEM?

06:33.727 --> 06:37.731
THE PROBLEM IS THAT THEY DON'T
KNOW HOW TO STYLE MY DAUGHTER.

06:37.764 --> 06:43.003
WHY IS IT THAT ALL YOU GAY MEN
HATE WOMEN SO MUCH?

06:43.036 --> 06:45.672
BECAUSE WE HAVE MOTHERS
LIKE YOU.

06:45.706 --> 06:47.708
OKAY, YOU, THE HAIR.

06:47.741 --> 06:50.444
SECURITY, THE MOTHER.

06:50.477 --> 06:51.645
I BEG YOUR PARDON?

06:51.678 --> 06:52.846
I WANT HER OFF MY SET.

06:52.880 --> 06:54.715
CONTROL FREAK.

06:54.748 --> 06:56.149
HORROR SHOW.

06:57.251 --> 07:00.854
I LOVE SHOW BUSINESS.

07:00.888 --> 07:02.656
♪♪ THOUGHT I HEARD
A CHICKEN SNEEZE ♪♪

07:02.689 --> 07:05.025
♪♪ SINGING POLLY WOLLY DOODLE
ALL THE DAY ♪♪

07:05.058 --> 07:07.761
♪♪ FARE THEE WELL,
FARE THEE WELL ♪♪
[ MICROPHONE FEEDBACK ]

07:07.794 --> 07:09.796
♪♪ FARE THEE WELL, MY FAIRY FAY ♪♪

07:09.830 --> 07:11.965
♪♪ FOR I'M GOIN' TO LOU'SIANA
FOR TO SEE MY SUSI‐ANNA ♪♪

07:11.999 --> 07:13.600
♪♪ SINGING POLLY WOLLY DOODLE
ALL THE DAY ♪♪

07:13.634 --> 07:14.568
YOU HAVE TO STOP!

07:14.601 --> 07:16.203
YEAH, YEAH. STOP.

07:16.236 --> 07:17.638
NOT TILL SILAS COMES OUT.

07:17.671 --> 07:19.072
THIS IS MY INVASION
OF PANAMA.

07:19.106 --> 07:20.674
LIKE WHEN WE GOT THE CANAL?

07:21.808 --> 07:23.143
NOW, WHAT DO THEY TEACH YOU
IN SCHOOL?

07:23.177 --> 07:24.878
HOW TO PASS
THE WEEKLY STANDARDIZED TESTS

07:24.912 --> 07:26.313
TO GET THE SCHOOL
MORE FUNDING.

07:26.346 --> 07:28.482
OKAY, KIDDO,
HOME SCHOOLING.

07:28.515 --> 07:31.685
UH, IN THE '80s,
PANAMA WAS RULED BY A MAN

07:31.718 --> 07:34.021
WITH BAD SKIN
NAMED MANUEL NORIEGA

07:34.054 --> 07:36.156
WHO USED TO BE OUR
PUPPET LEADER BUT THEN WASN'T.

07:36.190 --> 07:38.192
SO AS THE U.S.
ALWAYS SEEMS TO DO

07:38.225 --> 07:40.427
WHEN WE HAVE A PRESIDENT NAMED
BUSH, WE INVADED HIS COUNTRY.

07:40.460 --> 07:42.829
NOW, THEN NORIEGA HID OUT
IN THE VATICAN EMBASSY,

07:42.863 --> 07:45.432
BUT WE COULDN'T STORM IN THERE
'CAUSE THE POPE WOULD FREAK,

07:45.465 --> 07:47.434
SO INSTEAD WE BLASTED ROCK MUSIC
AT THE BUILDING

07:47.467 --> 07:49.570
TILL IT DROVE HIM SO CRAZY
THAT HE SURRENDERED.

07:49.603 --> 07:51.605
SILAS IS YOUR MOM'S NORIEGA,

07:51.638 --> 07:54.174
AND "POLLY WOLLY DOODLE"
IS HER ROCK 'N' ROLL.

07:55.709 --> 07:57.144
WOW.

07:57.177 --> 07:59.646
NOW I'M TIRED AGAIN.

07:59.680 --> 08:03.584
DID NORIEGA HAVE ACOUSTIC
NOISE‐CANCELING HEADPHONES?

08:03.617 --> 08:07.688
BECAUSE SILAS DOES, AND I DON'T,
AND NOW I'M GOING MENTAL.

08:07.721 --> 08:12.492
GO TO YOUR...MEDIOCRE PUBLIC
SCHOOL BEFORE YOU'RE LATE.

08:15.195 --> 08:17.130
IS IT OKAY
IF I STAY AFTER SCHOOL?

08:17.164 --> 08:18.732
I JOINED THE DEBATE CLUB.

08:19.833 --> 08:21.168
WHAT BROUGHT THAT ON?

08:21.201 --> 08:24.938
I DON'T KNOW. I THOUGHT
IT'D BE FUN TO DEBATE AND STUFF.

08:24.972 --> 08:26.740
WELL, GOOD FOR YOU.

08:26.773 --> 08:27.808
HAVE FUN.

08:27.841 --> 08:30.244
THANKS.

08:32.779 --> 08:38.318
SILAS, COME OUT, PLEASE.

08:38.352 --> 08:40.220
[ SIGHS ]

08:40.254 --> 08:43.724
I'M TRYING TO HELP YOU.

08:45.492 --> 08:48.795
OH, GOD DAMN IT.

08:48.829 --> 08:50.797
WHAT CAN I DO TO HELP YOU?

08:50.831 --> 08:52.232
BUY HIM A CAR.

08:53.100 --> 08:54.501
I WANT A CAR.

08:54.535 --> 08:56.703
NO.

09:03.410 --> 09:04.311
SO, HOW'S BUSINESS?

09:04.344 --> 09:06.413
I'M NOT GONNA TALK WITH YOU
ABOUT THIS.

09:06.446 --> 09:07.581
NOT SO HOT?

09:07.614 --> 09:10.484
JEEZ, NANCY, IF YOU CAN'T RAKE
IT IN DEALING DRUGS, THEN ‐‐

09:10.517 --> 09:11.852
I SWEAR.
COME ON.

09:11.885 --> 09:13.854
STOP THINKING OF ME LIKE A KID.
TALK TO ME.

09:13.887 --> 09:15.856
FINE. BUSINESS IS FINE.

09:15.889 --> 09:17.057
THANK YOU.

09:21.795 --> 09:23.263
SO, IS IT JUST WEED?

09:23.297 --> 09:25.999
ARE YOU SLINGING
COKE OR METH?

09:28.035 --> 09:29.870
JUST WEED.

09:29.903 --> 09:31.638
WHY?

09:31.672 --> 09:35.042
BECAUSE I THINK...

09:35.075 --> 09:37.544
COKE AND METH ARE...

09:37.578 --> 09:42.649
[ SIGHS ] DANGEROUS DRUGS
THAT DESTROY LIVES.

09:42.683 --> 09:47.354
I THINK POT‐SMOKING
IS BASICALLY A VICTIMLESS CRIME,

09:47.387 --> 09:48.956
ALTHOUGH I DON'T WANT YOU
SMOKING IT.

09:48.989 --> 09:50.824
YOU SHOULDN'T SMOKE IT.
POT MAKES YOU STUPID.

09:50.858 --> 09:53.794
YOU TWO LOOK LIKE
YOU ARE READY TO BUY.

09:53.827 --> 09:55.696
I ‐‐ I NEED SOMETHING
FOR MY SON.

09:55.729 --> 09:57.931
OH, SPECIAL OCCASION?

09:57.965 --> 09:58.932
BIRTHDAY? GRADUATION?

09:58.966 --> 10:00.834
MY GIRLFRIEND
JUST HAD AN ABORTION.

10:00.868 --> 10:02.970
I'VE GOT JUST THE CAR.

10:03.003 --> 10:04.571
THIS IS SWEET.

10:08.909 --> 10:10.544
TWO SEATER.

10:10.577 --> 10:13.046
NO BACKSEAT, NO TROUBLE.

10:14.781 --> 10:17.251
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

10:17.284 --> 10:18.552
I LOVE IT.

10:20.854 --> 10:23.123
NO. UNSAFE.

10:23.156 --> 10:24.992
IF YOU'RE SO CONCERNED
ABOUT MY SAFETY,

10:25.025 --> 10:27.461
MAYBE YOU SHOULD HAVE CONSIDERED
ANOTHER LINE OF WORK.

10:27.494 --> 10:29.429
ONE MORE WORD,
I'M TAKING MY DIRTY DRUG MONEY,

10:29.463 --> 10:31.932
AND I'M BUYING MYSELF DIAMOND
EARRINGS AND A GOLD TOOTH.

10:31.965 --> 10:33.667
MOM ‐‐
GET YOUR ASS
INTO A NICE FOUR‐DOOR

10:33.700 --> 10:35.469
AND BE GRATEFUL
YOU'RE NOT ON ROLLERBLADES.

10:35.502 --> 10:38.772
YOU CAN BUY THE SPORTS CAR
WHEN YOU'RE 47 AND BALD.

10:38.805 --> 10:40.741
[ SIGHS ]

10:40.774 --> 10:44.545
AGRESTIC ELEMENTARY HAS BECOME
A SECOND‐RATE DEBATE SCHOOL.

10:44.578 --> 10:50.050
WE WERE THE REGIONAL CHAMPIONS
WHEN STUDENTS LIKE JOEL GARRITY,

10:50.083 --> 10:55.889
LEON KRANTZBERG,
AND LARRY CHIN WERE DEBATING.

10:55.923 --> 10:58.959
BUT NOW IT'S UP TO YOU
TO UPHOLD THEIR LEGACY,

10:58.992 --> 11:01.962
TO MAKE US THE POWERHOUSE
WE ONCE WERE

11:01.995 --> 11:07.167
AND RETURN
THE DISRAELI AWARD HOME...

11:07.201 --> 11:11.538
♪♪ BUM BUM‐BUM BUM‐BUM BUM
BUM‐BUM BUM ♪♪

11:11.572 --> 11:18.745
♪♪ BUM BUM‐BUM BUM‐BUM BUM
BUM‐BUM BUM‐BUM ♪♪

11:20.814 --> 11:25.085
♪♪ BUM‐BUM BUM BUM BUM ♪♪

11:28.822 --> 11:33.026
♪♪ BUM‐BUM BUM BUM BUM ♪♪

11:36.897 --> 11:40.200
♪♪ BI‐BUM BUM BUM ♪♪

11:41.268 --> 11:44.538
♪♪ BI‐BUM BUM‐BUM ♪♪

11:44.571 --> 11:46.206
ISABEL.

11:46.240 --> 11:48.375
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU,
MR. WILSON.

11:48.408 --> 11:50.611
DOES YOUR MOTHER KNOW
YOU'RE HERE?
NO.

11:50.644 --> 11:51.979
AND PLEASE DON'T TELL HER.

11:52.012 --> 11:53.580
OH,
I DON'T SPEAK TO THAT CU‐‐

11:55.215 --> 11:56.850
YOUR MOTHER AND I
RARELY SPEAK.

11:56.884 --> 11:57.985
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.

11:58.018 --> 11:59.853
I NEED SOMEONE I TRUST
TO HANDLE MY MONEY.

11:59.887 --> 12:01.822
WHAT MONEY?
FROM MY COMMERCIALS.

12:01.855 --> 12:03.257
I'M THE NEW HUSKEROOS GIRL.

12:03.290 --> 12:05.259
OH, "THE BIGGER THE BETTER,
THE HUSKEROOS SWEATER"?

12:05.292 --> 12:06.827
YEAH, THAT'S GONNA BE ME.

12:06.860 --> 12:08.295
AND WE'RE TALKING
BIG HUNKS OF CHEDDAR.

12:08.328 --> 12:10.063
SO, CAN YOU HELP ME,
MR. WILSON?

12:10.097 --> 12:12.232
WELL, I COULD PUT YOUR MONEY
IN A TRUST,

12:12.266 --> 12:14.434
BUT YOU'RE GONNA NEED
AT LEAST ONE PARENT

12:14.468 --> 12:15.969
TO BE THE SIGNATORY
UNTIL YOU'RE 18.

12:16.003 --> 12:17.604
THAT'S BULLSHIT.
THE MONEY'S MINE.

12:17.638 --> 12:21.675
THE STATE OF CALIFORNIA SAYS
YOU GOT TO PICK ONE PARENT ‐‐
MY DAD.

12:23.644 --> 12:26.680
YOUR MOM REALLY HAS NO IDEA
THAT YOU'RE COMING TO ME?

12:31.718 --> 12:35.656
CAN YOUR ACCOUNTANT INTEREST YOU
IN A DELICIOUS CRUNCHIE?

12:35.689 --> 12:37.191
YAY.

12:38.926 --> 12:42.095
[ ISRAELI MUSIC PLAYS ]

12:59.313 --> 13:01.815
WHOO!

13:01.849 --> 13:04.351
[ APPLAUSE,
INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

13:07.754 --> 13:10.057
[ HUMS ISRAELI SONG ]

13:12.693 --> 13:15.429
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

13:16.930 --> 13:19.099
AHH.

13:20.033 --> 13:21.435
ARE YOU STILL ANGRY WITH ME?

13:21.468 --> 13:24.004
NO, I'M FINE.
I'M FINE WITH BEING A FRIEND.

13:24.037 --> 13:25.305
I'M A FINE FRIEND.

13:25.339 --> 13:26.340
HMM.

13:39.953 --> 13:41.622
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

13:41.655 --> 13:42.789
I HAVE TO FUCK YOU.

13:42.823 --> 13:44.892
WILL YOU STOP?

13:44.925 --> 13:46.660
I TOLD YOU.

13:46.693 --> 13:49.396
YOU DON'T HAVE THE QUALITIES
I LOOK FOR IN A MAN.

13:49.429 --> 13:51.098
NOW, WHAT EXACTLY
ARE THOSE QUALITIES?

13:51.131 --> 13:53.534
BECAUSE I CAN GET THEM.
I KNOW A GUY WHO KNOWS A GUY.

13:54.601 --> 13:56.470
I LIKE BIG MEN.

13:56.503 --> 14:00.073
YOU HAVE NONE
OF THE PHYSICAL QUALITIES

14:00.107 --> 14:02.342
I LOOK FOR
IN A MALE LOVER.

14:02.376 --> 14:03.744
[ SIGHS ]

14:03.777 --> 14:07.881
BUT YOU DO HAVE SOFT SKIN...

14:07.915 --> 14:10.317
AND SAD EYES.

14:10.350 --> 14:14.755
AND THOSE ARE THINGS
I FIND VERY ATTRACTIVE

14:14.788 --> 14:17.424
WHEN I SLEEP WITH WOMEN.

14:20.894 --> 14:22.229
OKAY.

14:22.262 --> 14:29.303
WELL, I DO SO APPRECIATE
HOW YOU RESPECT MY DIETARY LAWS.

14:29.336 --> 14:31.939
OH, IT'S FUN.

14:31.972 --> 14:34.942
[ CHUCKLES ]
LET'S EAT.

14:34.975 --> 14:36.810
LOOK AT THESE LAMB CHOPS.

14:36.844 --> 14:39.580
I LIKE PORK CHOPS, MYSELF.

14:41.114 --> 14:44.718
YOU KNOW,
THE PIG IS A FILTHY ANIMAL.

14:44.751 --> 14:49.656
IT CARRIES PARASITES THAT LIVE
IN YOUR INTESTINE AND LAY EGGS,

14:49.690 --> 14:51.592
CAUSING ALL KINDS OF ILLNESS.

14:51.625 --> 14:54.328
WELL, THEM PARASITES
TASTE DAMN GOOD TO ME.

14:54.361 --> 14:58.799
MISS VANEETA, I'M SIMPLY TRYING
TO EDUCATE YOU.

14:58.832 --> 15:00.701
WHY?
THIS AIN'T MUSLIM SCHOOL.

15:00.734 --> 15:01.835
THAT'S ENOUGH, LITTLE GIRL.

15:01.869 --> 15:04.171
PLEASE, HEYLIA,
LET ME TALK TO HER.

15:04.204 --> 15:08.876
YOUR HOSTILITY
HANGS THICK IN THE AIR.

15:08.909 --> 15:10.310
WHAT'S TROUBLING YOU?

15:10.344 --> 15:13.814
YOU COMIN' 'ROUND HERE WITH
YOUR HOLIER‐THAN‐THOU BULLSHIT.

15:13.847 --> 15:15.549
WE DON'T EAT THIS.
WE DON'T DO THAT.

15:15.582 --> 15:18.485
WE LIKE OUR WOMEN DRESSED
LIKE FUCKIN' BEEKEEPERS.

15:18.519 --> 15:20.220
[ BOWL SLAMS ON TABLE ]

15:24.691 --> 15:27.127
MY DEAR CHILD...

15:27.160 --> 15:30.230
MAYBE YOU NEED TO TAKE
A GOOD, HARD LOOK AT YOURSELF.

15:30.264 --> 15:35.435
LOOK AT YOUR TATTOOS,
YOUR CORNROWS.

15:35.469 --> 15:39.573
LISTEN TO THE LANGUAGE
THAT COMES OUT OF YOUR MOUTH.

15:39.606 --> 15:41.108
YOU'RE NOT A LADY.

15:41.141 --> 15:42.910
YOU DON'T ACT LIKE A LADY.

15:42.943 --> 15:45.879
AND THEN YOU WONDER WHY
YOUR BABY HAS NO FATHER.

15:45.913 --> 15:47.948
FUCK YOU, YOU BOW‐TIE‐WEARIN'
MOTHERFUCKER!

15:47.981 --> 15:50.484
HEY, NOW STOP, BOTH OF YOU.

15:50.517 --> 15:52.986
JUST ‐‐ LET'S JUST RELAX
AND HAVE A GOOD MEAL.

15:53.020 --> 15:56.390
I AM SORRY, HEYLIA.
PERHAPS I SHOULD BE GOING.

15:56.423 --> 15:59.426
THAT'S THE BEST WORDS COME OUT
OF YOUR FOOL MOUTH ALL NIGHT.

15:59.459 --> 16:01.061
JOSEPH.

16:01.094 --> 16:02.930
I'LL CALL YOU, HEYLIA.

16:02.963 --> 16:04.064
[ SCOFFS ]

16:07.034 --> 16:08.702
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

16:08.735 --> 16:10.137
YOU GOT ANY LAST WORDS?

16:10.170 --> 16:10.938
YES.

16:10.971 --> 16:12.539
WHERE THE HELL ARE YOU?

16:12.573 --> 16:15.442
YOU SO BUSY FINDING FUCKIN'
COUSCOUS ON THE INTERNET,

16:15.475 --> 16:17.544
YOU AIN'T TAKIN' CARE
OF YOUR GAME.

16:17.578 --> 16:20.080
CONRAD IS NEVER HERE NO MORE,
AND BUSINESS IS OFF,

16:20.113 --> 16:21.481
AND ALL YOU CAN THINK ABOUT

16:21.515 --> 16:23.851
IS SOME FANCY‐PREACHIN',
PORK‐FEARIN' FAT ASS.

16:23.884 --> 16:26.653
HEYLIA, IF YOU GON' DROP OUT

16:26.687 --> 16:29.223
AND BECOME ONE OF THEM
LEE‐LEE‐SHRIEKIN' ISLAM LADIES,

16:29.256 --> 16:31.458
LET ME KNOW SO I CAN HIRE
A FUCKIN' BABYSITTER

16:31.491 --> 16:33.260
AND CALL KEEYON IN
AND GET TO WORK,

16:33.293 --> 16:35.062
'CAUSE EVERYTHING
IS GOIN' TO SHIT.

16:35.095 --> 16:38.765
[ CHAIR SLIDES,
UTENSIL SLAMS ]

16:38.799 --> 16:40.634
COME ON.

16:52.346 --> 16:53.413
OH.

16:53.447 --> 16:54.882
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

16:54.915 --> 16:57.184
OH. OH.

16:58.285 --> 16:59.119
WHAT'S THAT?

16:59.152 --> 17:00.954
WHAT DOES IT LOOK LIKE?

17:00.988 --> 17:02.956
OH‐HO‐HO‐HO.

17:02.990 --> 17:04.858
YOU THINK YOU CAN TAKE IT?

17:04.892 --> 17:06.260
IT'S NOT FOR ME.

17:12.900 --> 17:14.968
GOD, IT'S BIG.

17:15.002 --> 17:17.905
I KNOW.

17:17.938 --> 17:20.140
[ LUBE SQUIRTS ]

17:20.174 --> 17:21.875
THAT'S REALLY BIG.

17:21.909 --> 17:23.243
IT'LL FIT.

17:25.946 --> 17:27.848
DOES IT HAVE TO BE BLACK?

17:27.881 --> 17:29.917
STOP BEING A PUSSY.

17:29.950 --> 17:32.152
I THOUGHT
THAT WAS THE WHOLE IDEA.

17:33.053 --> 17:35.122
DON'T FORGET TO BREATHE.

17:36.290 --> 17:39.526
[ SCHOOL BELL RINGS,
INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

17:47.367 --> 17:51.004
♪♪ BUM BUM BUM BUM BUM BUM BUM ♪♪

17:51.038 --> 17:54.174
♪♪ BUM BUM‐BUM BUM‐BUM
BUM BUM‐BUM BUM ♪♪

17:54.208 --> 18:03.016
♪♪ BUM BUM‐BUM BUM‐BUM BUM
BUM‐BUM BUM‐BUM ♪♪

18:03.050 --> 18:09.089
♪♪ BUM‐BUM BUM BUM BUM ♪♪

18:10.958 --> 18:12.159
WHAT?

18:12.192 --> 18:13.894
♪♪ BUM‐BUM BUM BUM BUM ♪♪

18:13.927 --> 18:17.064
HEY, CHECK IT OUT.

18:18.932 --> 18:20.133
OW!

18:21.134 --> 18:21.835
♪♪ BUM‐BUM BUM‐BUM ♪♪

18:21.869 --> 18:24.004
[ SCHOOL BELL RINGS ]

18:27.808 --> 18:30.143
♪♪ BUM‐BUM BUM‐BUM ♪♪

18:33.814 --> 18:36.149
HOW ARE THE KIDS?

18:38.552 --> 18:39.987
CONRAD.

18:40.921 --> 18:44.324
GOT 20 NEW CLIPPINGS.
WE'LL SEE HOW THEY DO.

18:48.395 --> 18:51.031
YOU'RE A GENIUS.

18:53.867 --> 18:54.902
WHAT'S WRONG?

18:54.935 --> 18:57.604
BEEN THINKING.

18:57.638 --> 18:59.606
ABOUT WHAT?

18:59.640 --> 19:00.874
[ SIGHS ]

19:00.908 --> 19:03.143
ABOUT OUR LITTLE MIRACLE.

19:03.177 --> 19:06.046
DEAD SMACK IN THE MIDDLE OF ALL
THESE HOUSES THAT GET BUSTED,

19:06.079 --> 19:07.614
AND WE SKATE.

19:07.648 --> 19:09.716
YEAH.

19:09.750 --> 19:12.786
WOW.

19:12.819 --> 19:16.023
WERE WE LUCKY.

19:16.056 --> 19:17.824
IT'S A FUNNY THING
ABOUT LUCK.

19:17.858 --> 19:19.026
WHAT'S THAT?

19:19.059 --> 19:20.427
I DON'T BELIEVE IN IT.

19:20.460 --> 19:22.563
YOU GOT SOMETHING
YOU WANT TO SAY TO ME?

19:22.596 --> 19:25.899
YOU WANT TO TELL ME WHY
OUR ARMENIAN PROBLEM IS
NO LONGER A PROBLEM?

19:25.933 --> 19:27.434
I TOLD YOU
I WAS GONNA TAKE CARE OF THEM.

19:27.467 --> 19:29.903
YOU'RE STILL FUCKIN'
THAT DEA GUY, AIN'T YOU?

19:29.937 --> 19:30.971
IT'S NOT LIKE THAT.

19:31.004 --> 19:32.739
THEN, PLEASE,
TELL ME WHAT IT'S LIKE.

19:32.773 --> 19:34.508
HE'S ON OUR SIDE.

19:34.541 --> 19:35.576
YOU FUCKIN' LIED TO ME.

19:35.609 --> 19:38.946
YOU SWORE ON YOUR CHILDREN
THAT HE DIDN'T KNOW.

19:38.979 --> 19:40.981
HE DIDN'T KNOW
WHEN I TOLD YOU.

19:41.014 --> 19:43.650
I MEAN, HE DID KNOW,
BUT I DIDN'T KNOW THAT HE KNEW.

19:43.684 --> 19:45.919
IT TURNED OUT, ACTUALLY,
THAT HE KNEW ALL ALONG,

19:45.953 --> 19:47.988
BUT IT DOES‐‐ IT'S ‐‐
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

19:48.021 --> 19:49.656
IT'S OKAY.

19:52.426 --> 19:54.828
HOW CAN YOU BE
SO FUCKIN' SURE?

19:54.862 --> 19:56.430
I HAVE INSURANCE.

19:56.463 --> 19:59.633
INSURANCE, WHA‐‐
STATE FARM GOT SOME "GET
OUT OF JAIL FREE" POLICY

19:59.666 --> 20:00.968
THAT I DON'T KNOW ABOUT?

20:01.001 --> 20:04.137
I ‐‐ I MARRIED HIM.

20:05.672 --> 20:07.774
YOU WHAT?

20:07.808 --> 20:09.610
WE'RE MARRIED.

20:11.545 --> 20:14.081
NO, IT'S REALLY CLEVER.

20:14.114 --> 20:15.616
SEE, IF I'M HIS WIFE,

20:15.649 --> 20:17.851
HE ‐‐ HE CAN'T BE FORCED
TO TESTIFY AGAINST ME,

20:17.885 --> 20:20.220
AND HE MARRIED A DRUG DEALER,

20:20.254 --> 20:23.323
SO IT'S KIND OF
MUTUALLY ASSURED DESTRUCTION.

20:23.357 --> 20:26.627
I HAVE THE MARRIAGE CERTIFICATE,
SO WE'RE PROTECTED.

20:30.864 --> 20:32.766
YOU'RE PROTECTED.

20:32.799 --> 20:34.735
AIN'T NO RING ON MY FINGER.

20:34.768 --> 20:36.603
WE'RE PARTNERS.

20:36.637 --> 20:37.771
WE'RE PARTNERS?

20:37.804 --> 20:42.109
THEN, WHY IS IT THAT EVERY MOVE
YOU MAKE DIGS MY GRAVE?

20:48.549 --> 20:50.484
HE DOESN'T KNOW ABOUT YOU.

20:50.517 --> 20:53.487
FOR HOW LONG?
IT'S JUST A MATTER OF TIME.

20:53.520 --> 20:54.821
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

20:54.855 --> 20:56.590
HOW IN THE FUCK
IS THIS GONNA BE OKAY?!

20:58.959 --> 21:00.360
YOU KNOW, HEYLIA WAS RIGHT.

21:00.394 --> 21:02.796
YOU JUST OPEN
YOUR BIG, BROWN EYES,

21:02.829 --> 21:04.765
AND ME,
I JUST FALL INTO SHIT!

21:08.869 --> 21:11.038
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

21:24.885 --> 21:27.588
WHAT IN THE HELL IS THIS?

21:27.621 --> 21:29.389
THE SOFTAIL DELUXE.

21:29.423 --> 21:30.991
WHAT THE FUCK IS IT DOING
IN MY ATRIUM?

21:31.024 --> 21:32.492
I BOUGHT IT. IT'S MINE.

21:32.526 --> 21:33.727
REALLY? WITH WHAT MONEY?

21:33.760 --> 21:34.928
MY SALARY.

21:34.962 --> 21:35.896
YOU GOT A JOB?

21:35.929 --> 21:37.197
YEAH.

21:37.231 --> 21:39.733
AND WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME?
DOING WHAT?

21:41.768 --> 21:44.605
I AM ISABEL'S MANAGER.

21:45.706 --> 21:47.007
OH, NO.

21:47.040 --> 21:50.010
NO. NO. NO.

21:50.043 --> 21:52.846
YES, I AM.
YES, YES, YES, YES, YES.

21:52.880 --> 21:54.314
YOU'RE A LAWYER, DEAN.

21:54.348 --> 21:56.483
YOU NEED TO GO FIND
LAWYER WORK.

21:56.517 --> 21:58.218
KILL ALL THE LAWYERS.

21:58.252 --> 22:00.053
GOD, HOW DID I GET HERE?

22:00.087 --> 22:02.422
WHAT HAVE I DONE?

22:02.456 --> 22:03.824
THIS IS NOT MY LIFE.

22:03.857 --> 22:06.627
"SAME AS IT EVER WAS."

22:24.878 --> 22:26.513
WHERE WERE YOU?

22:28.949 --> 22:32.686
DRIVING AROUND.

22:32.719 --> 22:34.021
IT FELT GOOD.

22:34.054 --> 22:38.592
SILAS...
IT'S 4:30 IN THE MORNING.

22:41.128 --> 22:42.863
YOU'RE NOT ALLOWED
TO STAY OUT THIS LATE.

22:42.896 --> 22:44.898
I KNOW. I'M SORRY.

22:44.932 --> 22:48.869
I'LL KEEP BETTER TRACK OF TIME
NEXT TIME.

22:48.902 --> 22:50.704
WELL...

22:53.507 --> 22:55.742
[ SIGHS ]

22:55.776 --> 22:58.846
GOOD.

22:58.879 --> 23:00.414
MOM?

23:00.447 --> 23:01.915
YEAH?

23:01.949 --> 23:04.251
WHAT YOU DO AND ALL...

23:04.284 --> 23:05.719
YEAH?

23:05.752 --> 23:08.522
...I'M COOL WITH IT.

23:23.303 --> 23:25.639
[ LAUGHTER ]

23:25.672 --> 23:29.142
Woman: FISH AND GAME OFFICIALS
TRANQUILIZED THE BEAR,

23:29.176 --> 23:32.346
WHO FELL OUT OF THE TREE
BUT WAS NOT INJURED.

23:32.379 --> 23:35.415
FISH AND GAME OFFICIALS
TRANQUILIZED THE BEAR,

23:35.449 --> 23:38.619
WHO FELL OUT OF THE TREE
BUT WAS NOT INJURED.

23:38.652 --> 23:42.089
[ Laughing ]
OH, WATCH THIS.

23:43.857 --> 23:47.694
Celia:
NO, WATCH THIS.

23:47.728 --> 23:49.363
WHERE'D YOU GET THIS?

23:49.396 --> 23:51.965
YOU E‐MAILED IT TO DEAN
AS A JOKE.

23:51.999 --> 23:54.034
OH, YEAH.
IT'S PRETTY FUNNY.

23:54.067 --> 23:56.570
WON'T BE SO FUNNY
WHEN I BULK‐MAIL IT

23:56.603 --> 23:58.005
TO EVERY VOTER IN AGRESTIC.

23:58.038 --> 24:01.708
OOH, I'M SHAKING.

24:01.742 --> 24:02.843
WELL, YOU SHOULD BE.

24:02.876 --> 24:04.244
BECAUSE WHEN I'M DONE,

24:04.278 --> 24:07.748
YOU WON'T BE ABLE TO GET A SEAT
IN A CHAIR FACTORY.

24:07.781 --> 24:09.850
UNLESS YOU PREFER
TO SAVE YOURSELF

24:09.883 --> 24:11.451
SOME MAJOR EMBARRASSMENT,

24:11.485 --> 24:14.154
NOT TO MENTION
POTENTIAL CRIMINAL CHARGES,

24:14.188 --> 24:18.692
BY MAKING ME THE SIGNATORY
ON ISABEL'S ACCOUNT

24:18.725 --> 24:21.628
INSTEAD OF HARLEY DAVIDSTEIN.

24:21.662 --> 24:22.863
ONLY NEEDED ONE PARENT,

24:22.896 --> 24:24.932
AND DAVIDSTEIN
BEAT YOU TO THE PUNCH.

24:24.965 --> 24:26.867
I WILL NOT ALLOW
YOU AND DEAN

24:26.900 --> 24:29.203
TO TAKE CONTROL
OF MY DAUGHTER'S FINANCES.

24:29.236 --> 24:31.872
I'M JUST FOLLOWING
HER ORDERS.
HER ORDERS?

24:31.905 --> 24:33.173
ISABEL CAME TO ME.

24:33.207 --> 24:36.410
AND I EXPLAINED TO HER
THAT SHE NEEDED TO MAKE A CHOICE

24:36.443 --> 24:39.046
BETWEEN YOU OR DEAN,
OR BOTH YOU AND DEAN.

24:39.079 --> 24:42.416
AND IT TOOK HER
HALF A SECOND TO DECIDE.

24:42.449 --> 24:43.517
REALLY?

24:43.550 --> 24:44.718
SHE HATES YOU.

24:45.886 --> 24:47.521
OH, MY GOD.
TOO BAD SHE CAN'T VOTE.

24:47.554 --> 24:51.091
WELL, I ‐‐ YOU KNOW, ISABEL
AND I HAVE HAD OUR DIFFERENCES.

24:51.124 --> 24:53.927
SHE HATES YOU.

24:53.961 --> 24:55.762
JUST LIKE I HATE YOU.

24:55.796 --> 24:56.897
SO YOU KNOW WHAT?

24:56.930 --> 24:59.600
GO AHEAD
AND BULK‐MAIL YOUR HEART OUT.

25:02.469 --> 25:04.204
SEE YA.

25:12.679 --> 25:14.515
HI.
WELCOME TO THURSDAY'S.

25:14.548 --> 25:15.415
HOW MANY?

25:15.449 --> 25:16.917
OH,
I'M HERE TO MEET SOMEONE.

25:16.950 --> 25:18.552
WELL,
WOULD YOU LIKE TO HAVE A SEAT?

25:27.694 --> 25:30.163
[ SIGHS ]

25:31.732 --> 25:33.467
HEY, THERE.
NANCY.

25:33.500 --> 25:35.736
Woman: WELCOME TO THURSDAY'S.
HOW MANY?

25:35.769 --> 25:37.638
TABLE FOR THREE.

25:41.575 --> 25:43.076
Nancy: OKAY.

25:43.110 --> 25:44.912
FIRST THINGS FIRST.

25:44.945 --> 25:46.547
I WANT TO APOLOGIZE.

25:46.580 --> 25:48.815
I DIDN'T THINK EITHER OF YOU
WOULD SHOW

25:48.849 --> 25:50.918
IF I TOLD YOU IN ADVANCE,
SO I LIED.

25:50.951 --> 25:52.286
I'M A LIAR.

25:52.319 --> 25:54.788
I'M SORRY, CONRAD.
I'M SORRY, PETER.

25:54.821 --> 25:57.424
THIS SHOULD HAVE HAPPENED
A LOT SOONER.

25:57.457 --> 26:00.060
THAT'S MY FAULT.
AGAIN, I APOLOGIZE.

26:00.093 --> 26:03.997
SO, IF YOU HAVE ANY ANGER,
SEND YOUR ANGER THIS WAY.

26:04.932 --> 26:08.802
NANCY, WHO IS THIS PERSON?

26:08.836 --> 26:11.738
THIS IS, UH, CONRAD,
MY BUSINESS PARTNER.

26:11.772 --> 26:13.006
WHOA.

26:13.040 --> 26:14.842
NO, I AM NOT.

26:14.875 --> 26:16.677
I AM JUST ANOTHER
OUT‐OF‐WORK BLACK MAN.

26:16.710 --> 26:20.214
I'VE NEVER SEEN THIS WOMAN
BEFORE IN MY LIFE.
IT'S OKAY.

26:20.948 --> 26:21.949
REALLY.

26:21.982 --> 26:23.217
WHY ARE WE HERE?

26:23.250 --> 26:26.887
CONRAD HAD SOME ISSUES
WITH OUR ARRANGEMENT,

26:26.920 --> 26:28.956
AND I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE BETTER
IF WE MET

26:28.989 --> 26:31.225
AND WE GOT TO KNOW EACH OTHER.

26:31.258 --> 26:34.127
CONRAD, THE FLOOR IS YOURS.

26:34.161 --> 26:35.729
ASK PETER ANYTHING.

26:35.762 --> 26:37.965
I DON'T THINK SO.
PETER, PLEASE.

26:37.998 --> 26:39.199
YOU'RE THE HUSBAND?

26:39.233 --> 26:40.667
I AM.

26:40.701 --> 26:43.971
AND YOU ARE THE PARTNER?

26:45.239 --> 26:46.139
CONRAD.

26:46.173 --> 26:48.575
WHY RISK YOUR WHOLE
FUCKIN' CAREER, MAN?

26:48.609 --> 26:52.012
I'M HAVING TROUBLE WRAPPING
MY HEAD AROUND THAT PART.

26:52.045 --> 26:53.347
I DO IT FOR HER.

26:53.380 --> 26:57.217
NOW IT'S MY TURN
TO HAVE A QUESTION ANSWERED.

26:57.251 --> 27:00.387
HOW DID
THIS PARTNERSHIP BEGIN?

27:00.420 --> 27:03.557
UM, MY KID BIT HER KID
AT A KARATE TOURNAMENT.

27:03.590 --> 27:05.526
OH, THAT'S FUNNY.
GUYS.

27:05.559 --> 27:07.160
YOUR BOYS AT THE DEA,
DO THEY KNOW ABOUT ME?

27:07.194 --> 27:09.463
I WOULDN'T KNOW.
PROBABLY NOT. YOU'RE SMALL‐TIME.

27:09.496 --> 27:11.899
NOBODY KNOWS ABOUT ANYBODY,
OKAY?

27:11.932 --> 27:15.736
CONRAD IS MY FRIEND
AND MY BUSINESS PARTNER.

27:17.104 --> 27:19.907
THIS WAS JUST SORT OF
DROPPED INTO MY LAP.

27:19.940 --> 27:21.909
I HAD NOT ANTICIPATED THIS.

27:21.942 --> 27:23.343
I KNOW. I'M SORRY.

27:23.377 --> 27:26.113
I THOUGHT WE SHOULD WORK THINGS
OUT SO WE COULD MOVE FORWARD.

27:26.146 --> 27:27.948
HOW THE FUCK IS THIS
SUPPOSED TO WORK OUT?

27:27.981 --> 27:29.516
WELL,
OFF THE TOP OF MY HEAD,

27:29.550 --> 27:33.587
I WOULD SAY DON'T EXPAND FURTHER
THAN THE GROW HOUSE,

27:33.620 --> 27:37.257
AND TAKE YOUR HARVEST DIRECTLY
TO THE MEDICAL MARIJUANA CLUBS.

27:37.291 --> 27:39.393
AND YOU DON'T WANT A PIECE?

27:39.426 --> 27:42.062
I DON'T WANT ANY MONEY.
I JUST WANT NANCY.

27:43.297 --> 27:44.798
AND I'M JUST SUPPOSED
TO TRUST YOU?

